Trade/Device Name(s): Bionexia™ hCG Pregnancy Serum/Urine Cassette and Dipstick Tests
Bionexia™M hCG Pregnancy Serum/Urine Cassette and Dipstick Tests
ADT's Bionexia™ hCG Pregnancy Serum/Urine Cassette and Dipstick Tests
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Bionexia hCG Pregnancy Serum/Urine Cassette and Dipstick Tests for visual, qualitative detection of hCG to aid in early determination of pregnancy.
Indications for Use Summary: Rapid chromatographic immunoassays for visual, qualitative detection of hCG in serum or urine specimens at 20 mIU/mL and above to aid in early determination of pregnancy; for healthcare professional use.
